Upon upgrading to 4.2.12.2 I encountered a few problems. My Home, cam and Call buttons stopped working. To make matters worse I did not receive any calls for 3 days!<br />
I resolved this awkward situation by retoring to my most stable version, which to me was 4.2.9.1, then applied the new IM APP(fixed) followed by 4.2.12.2. That fixed my issues. I hope it helps. I don&#8217;t have any partitioned sd card in case anyone wonders.<br />
God bless.</p>
