        <div id="dsq-comment-body-5533" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-5533" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>@siani_8<br />
Open that script (the cyanogen one) in the notepad and check the value by the variable called: linux_swap_en it should be (1) not zero. Then it will be working for you. I am not sure but I believe that there are defined some other setting you dont need like cpu speed etc. you might want to delete them if you like. Using terminal navigate to the location your userinit.sh is located and then type in: adb push userinit.sh /system/sd/userinit.sh<br />
Enjoy</p>
</div>
